ZALIAGIRIS
v.
ZALIAGIRIS. No. 332A04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 14, 2005. Preston O. Odom, III, Charlotte, for Elizabeth Smith Zaliagiris. Tate Sterrett, Kary C. Watson, Charlotte, for Thomas E. Zaliagiris.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 10th day of November 2005 by Plaintiff to Withdraw Appeal:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 14th day of November 2005."
